ner\">\n            <h3 style=\"font-family: var(--heading-font); font-size: 2.2em; margin-bottom: 40px; color: var(--primary-color);\">Get In Touch</h3>\n            <p>Have a question or looking for something specific? We'd love to hear from you!</p>\n            <p>Email: <a href=\"mailto:info@retrothreads.com\" style=\"color: var(--primary-color); font-weight: 700;\">info@retrothreads.com</a></p>\n            <p>Follow us on <a href=\"#\" style=\"color: var(--primary-color); font-weight: 700;\">Instagram</a> and <a href=\"#\" style=\"color: var(--primary-color); font-weight: 700;\">Facebook</a>!</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Retro Threads. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}